  description: "abc.ABCMeta.__instancecheck__ __defaults__ and identity checks in abcdefaults201 namespace — __instancecheck__.__defaults__ is None (NoneType) because __instancecheck__(self, instance) takes two required arguments with no defaults; __instancecheck__.__class__.__name__=='function'; __instancecheck__.__name__=='__instancecheck__' (len=17: 2 underscores + 'instancecheck'=13 + 2 underscores = 17); verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
